# Cloudflare Workers Static Assets headers.
#
# CORS on /assets/* so the splitea-shares worker — which serves
# the public share-link landing page at `/r/<id>` — can load
# the SPA cross-origin from a different host (e.g. the dev
# environment at splitea-shares-dev.raulmoracolon.workers.dev).
# `<script type="module">` cross-origin loads require an
# Access-Control-Allow-Origin response header, otherwise Safari
# silently blocks the module and #root stays empty (black
# screen on the recipient's device).
/assets/*
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *
  Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: cross-origin
